OL,3,CJude Bellingham still 'proud' of World
OL,4,CCup run, despite semi-final heartbreak
OL,6,FJude Bellingham says his overriding
OL,7,Femotion is pride after England's World
OL,8,FCup semi-final defeat against
OL,9,FArgentina.
OL,11,FThe Stourbridge-born star told ITV
OL,12,FNews: "I think the one kind of thing
OL,13,Fthat's overriding for me is pride.
OL,15,F"Proud to represent my nation and
OL,16,Fproud to have given them a few good
OL,17,Fmoments along the way.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784222320
OL,3,CJude Bellingham still 'proud' of World
OL,4,CCup run, despite semi-final heartbreak
OL,6,F"Yeah, I know I'll be back, and we'll
OL,7,Fbe back, and we'll give everything
OL,8,Fwe've got to try and bring it home for
OL,9,Fus."
OL,11,FBellingham was a star of the
OL,12,Ftournament, scoring six goals,
OL,13,Fincluding netting both in the quarter-
OL,14,Ffinal against Norway.
OL,16,FHe was the first player to score two
OL,17,Fgoals in consecutive knockout stage
OL,18,Fgames at a single World Cup since
OL,19,FDiego Maradona in 1986.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
