FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784222320
OL,3,CJude Bellingham still 'proud' of World
OL,4,CCup run, despite semi-final heartbreak
OL,6,FThe midfielder, who plays for Spanish
OL,7,Fgiants Real Madrid, has been selected
OL,8,Ffor the Freedom of Dudley Borough
OL,9,Faward alongside his teammate Morgan
OL,10,FRogers, who is from Halesowen.
OL,12,FThe pair were also painted as a mural
OL,13,Fon the side of a fish and chip shop in
OL,14,FQuinton.
OL,16,FRogers said his mum sent him a photo
OL,17,Fof the artwork. He said: "It's really
OL,18,Fnice. It's a cool thing that they've
OL,19,Fdone.
OL,26,@yD@ZOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784222320
OL,3,CJude Bellingham still 'proud' of World
OL,4,CCup run, despite semi-final heartbreak
OL,6,F"Obviously, I know the area, and I
OL,7,Fknow the place where it is, so it's
OL,8,Freally cool that they can do that for
OL,9,Fus."
OL,11,FBellingham joined Birmingham City at
OL,12,Funder-8s level and became the club's
OL,13,Fyoungest first-team player when he
OL,14,Fmade his senior debut at the age of 16.
OL,16,FThe 23-year-old has now made more than
OL,17,F50 appearances for England.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
