OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784222320
OL,3,CJude Bellingham still 'proud' of World
OL,4,CCup run, despite semi-final heartbreak
OL,6,FSpeaking after their loss on 15 July,
OL,7,FBellingham said: "I think all the lads
OL,8,Fhave done everything we could over the
OL,9,Fcourse of the tournament.
OL,11,F"You can't fault the effort and the
OL,12,Ffight and all of those things.
OL,14,F"That's the life, I suppose, of a
OL,15,Ffootballer at this level - the more
OL,16,Fbeautiful a journey is, the more
OL,17,Fheartbreaking the end is.
OL,19,F"I'm really proud of all my teammates.
OL,20,FI think they put in a magnificent
OL,21,Fshift over the past few weeks."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
