CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784222320
OL,3,CJude Bellingham still 'proud' of World
OL,4,CCup run, despite semi-final heartbreak
OL,6,FBut despite the heartbreaking defeat,
OL,7,FBellingham has been called an all-time
OL,8,Fgreat after his performance throughout
OL,9,Fthe competition.
OL,11,FHe's joined Harry Kane and Gary
OL,12,FLineker as one of just three England
OL,13,Fplayers to score at least five goals
OL,14,Fat a single World Cup.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/6
